{"tid":915233,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一票，要求出多個扔麵粉慶祝生日icon","createTime":"2018-11-24T21:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T06:50:19.000Z","uid":7790,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11b30fabaa914004334756ac6477ad74e3573561","tid":915233,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T21:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96b58f4c5593566cdcacdfdb715f0f2ee4b4ccc","tid":915233,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T21:36:23.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=8zFlkMM53qITZ6U1f%2FK3gAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7fa49cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"58590cc2130f121b2df8b4e8c398a3e0fc3018be","tid":915233,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11b30fabaa914004334756ac6477ad74e3573561","tid":915233,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T21:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T22:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41121b040da87c14c04c0d4374c43ae445a319c0","tid":915233,"uid":61211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T22:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8248bf04fe46db30cd99e1f0b9e97a4e9020ae","tid":915233,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Boom"},{"pid":"2f90fff7e8cbcd7c3a704ab11c56555ed1309d4e","tid":915233,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:24:36.000Z","msg":"強烈要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f002544742764222fe880b4c8bce0cb4c11e075","tid":915233,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6266ba6b4eb77872d4225888d6a47e0391225c3f","tid":915233,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扔麵粉"}]}